<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/48986527-travis">Travis</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It&apos;s based on the author&apos;s real life. There are good things and bad things that happen, but the ending doesn&apos;t ruin the effort you put in reading the <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It's based on the author's real life. There are good things and bad things that happen, but the ending doesn't ruin the effort you put in reading the rest of the book. In fact, you'll probably want to read the end after reading the beginning. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
